*Izvinjavam* se zbog mog ponasanja. (I apologize for my behaviour.)

Molim te, *izvinjavam* se za sve sto sam ucinio. (Please, I apologize for everything I have done.)

Ona je *izvinjavala* se za gresku. (She was apologizing for her mistake.)

Jedno dete je *izvinjavalo* se za kasni odlazak. (One child was apologizing for being late.)

Njegovo pokajanje je bilo iskreno, pa je *izvinjavao* se nastavniku. (His repentance was sincere, so he was apologizing to the teacher.)